# Setting up Project Dependencies

## 1. Vite
[Vite](https://vitejs.dev/) is a build tool designed to offer a faster and more streamlined development experience for modern web projects.

```bash
npm create vite@latest

##2.Tailwind
Tailwind is a utility-first CSS framework, providing a range of pre-defined classes for quick and flexible design implementation directly in your markup.
```bash
npm install -D tailwindcss
npx tailwindcss init
